---
title: Surf’s Up Chicken & Rice Bowls with Kiwi Salsa & Chipotle Lime Crema
description: Can’t get enough of sweet and savory flavor combos? These bowls are just the thing. Here, we sear chicken breast strips with a bevy of warming, smoky spices, then serve over scallion-flecked rice with a drizzle of chipotle lime crema. An easy kiwi and tomato salsa adds sweet, fresh contrast and bright color, taking the dish to the next level. One bite will have you totally BOWL-ed over.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tropical-chicken-bowls-0a73bdb2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/surfs-up-chicken-rice-bowls-6019715d75a1df47d4055154-c392659f.pdf
time required: 20 minutes
